Be careful to avoid hearing loss or damage by careless use of earphones. Continuous usage at high sound levels can lead to deterioration of hearing capacity.  A rough estimate to tell if the volume of your headphones is too loud is when a person standing near you can hear the music through your headphones.  Points to follow: Don't use headphones for long periods at a stretch. If necessary, take short breaks at regular intervals.  Never listen to music at 100% volume levels. Use 60% volume for 60 minutes and then take a break.  Use good quality gear. Over the ear headphones with noise cancelling features are useful for relatively longer listening time.  Protective ear equipments are also available in case prolonged exposure is a must.  Like this info? Just send us a message to join our WhatsApp group.

- The concept of pornographic films  Pornographic films are those films that show scenes of men and women without their bodies and without respect for public morals, either by looking at their naked bodies and bodies, or by portraying them in scenes where they have sexual relations. The viewer watches these films through a variety of technology, such as television, smartphones, or computers. [1] The long stare of these films, apart from their content, can lead to eye strain, impaired vision, wasted time . [2]   - Damages of watching pornographic films to watch pornographic films are a lot of damage, both to the individual himself and to his community.    - Damage caused by the individual ..  Cause problems in connection and communication with the husband and life partner. [3] The addict is put in a fantasy far from reality, and makes sex has a virtual process, affecting his relationship with the life partner to become a relationship only sex, And may subsequently cause the addict to fail in his or her marital relationship. [4] Pornography and addiction may cause an addict to engage in other sexual acts that may eventually lead to illness due mainly to those behaviors and forbidden relationships , As a disease AIDS, and gonorrhea. [3] The life partner is embarrassed if the addict attempts to perform the pornographic passages he or she sees, because these passages are not entirely logical and realistic. [3] Cause problems with a partner Life to dislike the other partner, regardless of the partner reached the maximum capacity to satisfy, to see the addict that his partner is unable to satisfy him sexually as those films. [5] Cause the non-addicted to the natural excitement resulting from sexual behavior inherent, because of his vision of the material Pornography is commonplace. [3] Cause embarrassment to life partner in case (3) may cause a deterioration in the economic situation of the addicted person, because of his constant pursuit of movies and pornography, which is not satisfied by what he saw, (3) cause damage to the work of the addict and his job; because of his absence or follow-up of these materials on the workplace. [3] cause psychological pressure on women if they see pornographic films before marriage , Which makes her contempt and humiliation for herself and femininity, a promise [6] According to a study conducted by researchers at the Max Planck Institute in Berlin, the capital of Germany, the Institute for Human Development, they found a difference in the size of the part of the brain (striatum) in men Addicted to pornographic movies which is smaller compared to men who do not watch. It is important to note that this part of the brain stimulates, stimulates and rewards the brain. They also found a deterioration in the frontal cortex in a positive relationship and watching pornographic films. [3] They cause young people to purchase and consume sex stimuli excessively so that they can agree between what they see and reality. The misuse of these stimulants leads to abnormal blood flow, The body, which causes the body to return and the amount of blood flowing from eating, is causing addiction because it will not reach a situation that satisfies it and is satisfied with it only by repeatedly eating. [6] May cause erectile dysfunction in men due to the bad mental state that engulfs The addict, which makes him unable to respond to any natural effect, and this increases the burden on his partner, which works to raise and attract even if it is a lot of beauty. [7] cause harm to men; married or not, because it may infect them with organic diseases , Such as prostatitis, urinary tract infection that leads to involuntary night urination, genital congestion, and enlarged prostate at an early age. [6]

ðŸ˜„à¤¬à¤¾à¤ª â€“ à¤¬à¥‡à¤Ÿà¤¾ à¤…à¤—à¤° à¤¸à¤¸à¥à¤°à¤¾à¤² à¤µà¤¾à¤²à¥‡ à¤¸à¥à¤•à¥‚à¤Ÿà¤° à¤¦à¥‡ à¤¤à¥‹ à¤•à¤¾à¤°ðŸš— à¤®à¤¾à¤‚à¤—à¤¨à¤¾, à¤•à¥‚à¤²à¤° à¤¦à¥‡ à¤¤à¥‹ AC à¤®à¤¾à¤‚à¤—à¤¨à¤¾,  à¤˜à¤° à¤¦à¥‡ à¤¤à¥‹ à¤¬à¤‚à¤—à¤²à¤¾ à¤®à¤¾à¤—à¤¨à¤¾..  à¤¬à¥‡à¤Ÿà¤¾â€“ à¤ªà¤¾à¤ªà¤¾ à¤…à¤—à¤° à¤µà¥‹ à¤²à¥œà¤•à¥€ à¤¦à¥‡ à¤¤à¥‹ à¤‰à¤¸à¤•à¥€ à¤®à¤¾à¤ à¤•à¥‹ à¤­à¥€ à¤®à¤¾à¤à¤— à¤²à¥‚ à¤•à¥à¤¯à¤¾? ðŸ˜º   à¤¬à¤¾à¤ª à¤–à¥à¤¶à¥€ à¤•à¥‡ à¤®à¤¾à¤°à¥‡ à¤¬à¥‡à¤¹à¥‹à¤¶ ðŸ˜³ðŸ˜‚ðŸ˜‚ðŸ˜ðŸ˜ðŸ˜ŽðŸ˜ŽðŸ˜œ
à¤ªà¤¤à¤¿ ðŸ‘¨ðŸ½: à¤¬à¤¾à¤¬à¤¾, à¤®à¥‡à¤°à¥€ à¤¬à¥€à¤µà¥€ à¤¬à¤¹à¥à¤¤ à¤ªà¤°à¥‡à¤¶à¤¾à¤¨ à¤•à¤°à¤¤à¥€ à¤¹à¥ˆà¥¤ à¤•à¥‹à¤ˆ à¤¹à¤² à¤¬à¤¤à¤¾à¤“, à¤•à¥à¤¯à¤¾ à¤•à¤°à¥‚à¤‚ ?  à¤¬à¤¾à¤¬à¤¾ ðŸŽ…ðŸ¿: à¤¬à¥‡à¤Ÿà¤¾, à¤…à¤—à¤° à¤¬à¥€à¤µà¥€ à¤•à¤¾ à¤•à¥‹à¤ˆ à¤¹à¤² à¤¹à¥‹à¤¤à¤¾, à¤¤à¥‹ à¤†à¤œ à¤®à¥ˆà¤‚ à¤¬à¤¾à¤¬à¤¾ à¤¨ à¤¹à¥‹à¤¤à¤¾ !  ðŸ˜«ðŸ˜«ðŸ˜«ðŸ˜©ðŸ˜«ðŸ˜©ðŸ˜¤
à¤²à¤¡à¤¼à¤•à¥€: "à¤­à¥ˆà¤¯à¤¾, à¤¸à¥à¤•à¥‚à¤Ÿà¥€ à¤•à¤¾ à¤¬à¥à¤°à¥‡à¤• à¤–à¤°à¤¾à¤¬ à¤¹à¥‹ à¤—à¤¯à¤¾ à¤¹à¥ˆ."  à¤®à¥ˆà¤•à¥‡à¤¨à¤¿à¤•: "à¤¬à¥à¤°à¥‡à¤• à¤ à¥€à¤• à¤¹à¥ˆ à¤®à¥ˆà¤¡à¤®, à¤†à¤ªà¤•à¤¾ à¤¸à¥ˆà¤‚à¤¡à¤² à¤˜à¤¿à¤¸ à¤—à¤¯à¤¾ à¤¹à¥ˆ." à¤²à¤¡à¤•à¥€: Ok sorry  ðŸ˜‚ðŸ˜‚ðŸ˜ðŸ˜ðŸ˜ðŸ˜ðŸ˜ðŸ˜
à¤¤à¤¾à¤Š à¤…à¤¸à¥à¤ªà¤¤à¤¾à¤² à¤—à¤¯à¤¾   à¤¡à¥‰à¤•à¥à¤Ÿà¤°à¤¨à¥€: à¤à¤• à¤²à¤‚à¤¬à¥€ à¤¸à¤¾à¤‚à¤¸ à¤²à¥‹  à¤¤à¤¾à¤Š à¤¨à¥‡ à¤à¤• à¤²à¤‚à¤¬à¥€ à¤¸à¤¾à¤‚à¤¸ à¤²à¥‡ à¤²à¥€   à¤¡à¥‰à¤•à¥à¤Ÿà¤°à¤¨à¥€: à¤•à¥à¤¯à¤¾ à¤®à¤¹à¤¸à¥‚à¤¸ à¤¹à¥à¤†   à¤¤à¤¾à¤Š: à¤•à¥Œà¤¨ à¤¸à¤¾ à¤ªà¤°à¤«à¥à¤¯à¥‚à¤® à¤²à¤—à¤¾ à¤•à¤° à¤†à¤ˆ à¤¹à¥ˆ à¤®à¤œà¤¾ à¤† à¤—à¤¯à¤¾ ðŸ˜†ðŸ˜€ðŸ˜†ðŸ˜€ðŸ˜€
à¤¸à¤¾à¤¸ à¤¨à¥‡ à¤¨à¤ˆ à¤¨à¤µà¥‡à¤²à¥€  à¤¬à¤¹à¥ à¤•à¥‹ à¤¸à¤®à¤à¤¾à¤¤à¥‡  à¤¹à¥à¤¯à¥‡  à¤•à¤¹à¤¾  - " à¤¦à¥‡à¤–à¥‹ à¤¬à¤¹à¥ !à¤®à¥ˆà¤‚  à¤‡à¤¸ à¤˜à¤° à¤•à¥€  à¤ªà¥à¤°à¤§à¤¾à¤¨à¤®à¤‚à¤¤à¥à¤°à¥€  à¤¹à¥‚à¤à¥¤à¤¤à¥à¤®à¥à¤¹à¤¾à¤°à¥‡  à¤¸à¤¸à¥à¤° à¤—à¥ƒà¤¹ à¤®à¤‚à¤¤à¥à¤°à¥€  à¤¹à¥ˆà¤‚à¥¤à¤¤à¥à¤®à¥à¤¹à¤¾à¤°à¤¾  à¤ªà¤¤à¤¿ à¤¯à¤¾à¤¨à¥€  à¤®à¥‡à¤°à¤¾  à¤¬à¥‡à¤Ÿà¤¾  à¤†à¤ªà¥‚à¤°à¥à¤¤à¤¿ à¤®à¤‚à¤¤à¥à¤°à¥€ à¤¹à¥ˆà¥¤à¤¤à¥à¤®à¥à¤¹à¤¾à¤°à¥€  à¤¨à¤¨à¤¦ à¤¯à¤¾à¤¨à¥€  à¤®à¥‡à¤°à¥€  à¤¬à¥‡à¤Ÿà¥€  à¤¯à¥‹à¤œà¤¨à¤¾  à¤®à¤‚à¤¤à¥à¤°à¥€ à¤¹à¥ˆà¥¤ à¤¤à¥à¤® à¤•à¥Œà¤¨ à¤¸à¤¾ à¤µà¤¿à¤­à¤¾à¤—  à¤²à¥‹à¤—à¥€ ?" à¤¬à¤¹à¥  -" à¤®à¤¾à¤ à¤œà¥€  ! à¤®à¥ˆà¤‚  à¤¤à¥‹ à¤µà¤¿à¤ªà¤•à¥à¤· à¤®à¥‡ à¤°à¤¹à¥‚à¤‚à¤—à¥€  à¤”à¤° à¤†à¤ªà¤•à¥€ à¤¸à¤°à¤•à¤¾à¤°  à¤¨à¤¹à¥€à¤‚  à¤šà¤²à¤¨à¥‡ à¤¦à¥‚à¤‚à¤—à¥€à¥¤" ðŸ˜œðŸ˜œðŸ˜œðŸ˜œðŸ˜œðŸ˜œ à¤¨à¤¯à¤¾ à¤¹à¥ˆ à¤¸à¤­à¥€ à¤•à¥‹ à¤­à¥‡à¤œà¥‹
